description:
Danny recaps this week's episode of The Real Housewives of New York, which features a winery visit, Sonja trying to steal some kisses, covert ciggs with the Countess, Ramona's plasma/diarrhea drama, fosé, animal prints, and facetiming with Garth/a bank teller.
